description:
Single Row || Spacious Living || Ready To Move
Villa for rent in Palma, Arabian Ranches 2
Living in Arabian Ranches 2 means stepping into a world where space and serenity meet modern convenience. This substantial 5-bedroom, 6-bathroom villa stretches across 6,874 sqft, offering an ideal canvas for those who crave both room to breathe and the freedom to design their own sanctuary. Unfurnished yet brimming with potential, it’s ready for you to infuse it with personality and luxury. The layout unfolds thoughtfully, guiding you through wide corridors and expansive rooms that encourage both daily living and grand entertaining. Each bedroom is generously sized, providing ample space for comfortable furniture arrangements, while the bathrooms—six in total—promise practicality and elegance. The heart of the home is a versatile living area, perfect for family gatherings or quiet evenings, complemented by a dining space that can accommodate gatherings of all sizes. Beyond comfort and layout, this villa is equipped with features that elevate everyday life. Central A/C ensures a comfortable climate year-round, while built-in wardrobes in each bedroom offer smart, space-saving storage. Step outside onto your private balcony—a quiet retreat for morning coffee or evening relaxation—and feel the calm of suburban living. The property also includes covered parking, keeping vehicles safe and accessible, and welcomes pets, making it an ideal home for animal lovers. Residents enjoy access to a shared pool and a modern gym, fostering a healthy, active lifestyle without leaving the community. Arabian Ranches 2 itself is a family-oriented haven. With landscaped gardens, walking paths, and children’s play areas, the neighborhood encourages outdoor living and community connection. It’s a peaceful escape yet well-connected;
